overview: Turn your head and cough! These sexy doctors have amazing bedside manners and will take care of all your aches and pains. Dr. Wesley Woods and Dr. Michael Roman know how to probe what needs to be probed. Male Nurse Colby Tucker makes amazing house calls and he even shows the janitor how to make a mess. No need to call 911 because these doctors have you covered.
